reviewText: The movies were sold at a great price, packaged according to their descriptions, and arrived 2 days early to my friend's home.
Total waste of money. I wish I could have given less than one star. I watched half of the first 2 movies. The first half being the only half that was actually on the dvd. Very disappointing.
If you are an Arnold fan, why not have.
Not a boxed set.  Came as separate movies packaged individually
I was very satisfied with the movies.
I have collected all of his DVDs in this series. I am a fan
Thanks for having this!  I am proud to add this to my DVD collection!
My grandson was happy to have them
